{
  "stem": "8784.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the commandant wanted to know is-- is which SS guard was there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had absolutely no trouble at pointing at one of the SS guards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whether she was the one or not didn't make any difference to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We simply pointed to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it tells a little bit about the time and place and that we did have a chance even with a lie-- was a-- was a violation of rules and all this because all this commandant did is chew out this SS guard-- this SS lady guard rather than hurt us at all.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were put back into the formation of the rest of the inmates, and nothing ever happened to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was one of those incidents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Another incident I remember in this camp is when-- and at that time, the rumor mill was working tremendously.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever was happening to Schindler-- to Schindler was very important news to us because we somehow knew that if anything happens to Schindler, we are in danger, that this was already like, you know, above board.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We already knew it, that Schindler is our keeper, that--.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And rumor had it one day that Schindler was called to the SS headquarters in-- in some place not far away in the city near where we were to respond to a charge that we had more food in this camp than the populations, of the Czechoslovak population outside of this camp.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- the way I remember that event is that we were locked in-- in the-- we were not locked in, but we were in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were standing practically by the doorways and windows waiting, hoping that Schindler is going to return.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
